p: The antigenic properties of all strains of influenza A(H1N1)pdm09 virus (including 17 isolates from lethal cases of the disease) were similar to the A/Michigan/45/2015 vaccine strain, strains of influenza B/Yamagata-like virus (3 of which were isolated from lethal cases of the disease) were similar to the B/Phuket/3073/2013 vaccine strain, and two strains of influenza B/Victoria-like virus were similar to the B/Brisbane/60/2008 vaccine strain.
